https://github.com/tonnyblair62/demo.git


## Installation / Setup instruction
* Open Terminal {Ctrl+Alt+T}

* git clone ```https://github.com/tonnyblair62/demo.git```

* cd Akan-Names

* code . or atom . based on the text editor you have.

